OL,3,CWhat do new official figures tell us
OL,4,Cabout UK job market?
OL,6,FHere's everything you need to know.
OL,8,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,9,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,10,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,11,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,13,FHow far have vacancies dropped?
OL,15,FOpen positions in the UK dropped by
OL,16,F28,000 to 705,000 in the three months
OL,17,Fto April, making it the lowest number
OL,18,Fof available opportunities since 2021.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
