OL,3,CWhat do new official figures tell us
OL,4,Cabout UK job market?
OL,6,FThe number of vacancies is now 10.6%
OL,7,Flower than it was before the Covid
OL,8,Fpandemic, the ONS said.
OL,10,FOutside of the pandemic, the last time
OL,11,Fthere were fewer than 705,000
OL,12,Fvacancies in the UK was in 2014.
OL,14,FWhich industries have been worst hit -
OL,15,Fand why?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
