OL,3,CWhat do new official figures tell us
OL,4,Cabout UK job market?
OL,6,FWholesale and retail trade, motor
OL,7,Frepair, hospitality and food services,
OL,8,Fthe arts, entertainment and recreation
OL,9,Fsector, real estate and electricity,
OL,10,Fgas, steam and air conditioning supply
OL,11,Fhave seen the biggest decreases,
OL,12,Faccording to the ONS.
OL,14,FFeedback from the ONS survey said some
OL,15,Fcompanies "may not be recruiting
OL,16,Fbecause of economic and geopolitical
OL,17,Funcertainty".
OL,19,FArtificial Intelligence has also been
OL,20,Fwidely blamed for staff cut backs in
OL,21,Fthe UK and elsewhere.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
