OL,3,CWhat do new official figures tell us
OL,4,Cabout UK job market?
OL,6,FAlso on Tuesday, London-based banking
OL,7,Fgiant Standard Chartered said it plans
OL,8,Fto cut around 7,800 jobs as it ramps
OL,9,Fup the use of AI across its operations.
OL,11,FIt is the latest firm to cut back its
OL,12,Fstaff numbers in favour of increased
OL,13,Fautomation and adoption of new
OL,14,Ftechnologies.
OL,16,FHas the unemployment rate changed?
OL,18,FBritain's rate of unemployment
OL,19,Funexpectedly rose to 5% in the three
OL,20,Fmonths to March - up from 4.9% in the
OL,21,Fthree months to February.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
