OL,3,CWhat do new official figures tell us
OL,4,Cabout UK job market?
OL,6,FMost economists had expected the rate
OL,7,Fto be unchanged.
OL,9,FLast month the Bank of England
OL,10,Fpredicted that unemployment would rise
OL,11,Fto 5.5% in 2027, even in its most
OL,12,Fpositive forecast.
OL,14,FThe more extreme impact scenario is
OL,15,Fforecast to be 5.6%.
OL,17,FAre wages keeping pace with inflation?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
