OL,3,CWhat do new official figures tell us
OL,4,Cabout UK job market?
OL,6,FEmployees average regular earnings,
OL,7,Fnot including bonuses, went up by 3.4%
OL,8,Fbetween January and March 2026 - but
OL,9,Fin real terms the amount was far less.
OL,11,FWhen adjusted in line with inflation,
OL,12,Fthe ONS calculated wages actually only
OL,13,Frose by 0.1% across the period.
